---
import AppLayout from "../../layouts/AppLayout.astro";
---

<AppLayout
  title="Privacy Policy - Tam Listen"
  description="Privacy policy for Tam Listen. A local-first audio player that keeps your data on your device."
>
  <main class="py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8"
        style="
        background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #CEDA8E 70%, #97A859 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      "
      >
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>

      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-12">Effective date: March 15, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Tam Listen is built by tambuzztam LLC. This policy describes how we
          handle your data.
        </p>

        <h2
          class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4"
          style="color: #CEDA8E;"
        >
          The short version
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Tam Listen is a local-first app. Your listening data stays on your
          device. We don't have accounts, we don't track you, and we can't see
          your library.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Data stored on your device
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          All of your data — listening progress, project organization, and
          playback metadata — is stored locally on your device. Your media files
          remain wherever you store them. We do not have access to any of it.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Cloud services
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          If you choose to import files from cloud providers such as iCloud
          Drive, Google Drive, or Dropbox, the app accesses them through the iOS
          Files picker. Your credentials are handled by those providers, not by
          us. We never receive or store your cloud service credentials.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Data from these services is accessed only when you explicitly initiate
          a file selection and is never shared with any party other than the
          provider you choose.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Analytics
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We do not collect any analytics or usage data. We use Apple's built-in
          App Analytics, which provides us with aggregate, anonymous information
          like download counts and crash reports. This data cannot be used to
          identify you. You can opt out of sharing this data in your device's
          privacy settings.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Data we don't collect
        </h2>
        <ul class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8 list-none pl-0 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: #97A859;">✓</span> No personal information
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: #97A859;">✓</span> No account registration
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: #97A859;">✓</span> No tracking across
            apps or websites
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: #97A859;">✓</span> No advertising
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Support
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          If you contact us for support, we'll receive your email address and
          message. We use this only to respond to you and don't add you to any
          marketing lists.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Changes to this policy
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We may update this policy from time to time. We'll post changes here,
          and the effective date will reflect when changes were made.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4" style="color: #CEDA8E;">
          Contact
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Questions? Reach us at <a
            href="mailto:support@tam.buzz"
            class="privacy-link">support@tam.buzz</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
        <a
          href="/listen"
          class="privacy-link inline-flex items-center transition-colors"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
          </svg>
          Back to Tam Listen
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</AppLayout>

<style>
  .privacy-link {
    color: #ceda8e;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .privacy-link:hover {
    color: #97a859;
  }
</style>
